title: World of Warcraft Valkors Gold Guide
description:
Valkor's Gold Making Guide for World of Warcraft. 
I saw this wasn't on The Pirate Bay, so I decided to be nice and upload it for all you people. This only includes the .pdf file, not the audio or website features. 
If you like it, then seed it! Because I won't. :(
Have fun making gold! ;)
EDIT 11/3/08: This is clean, I've scanned it with the McAfee, Avast!, and AVG antiviruses. No files altered, and just letting you guys know, this is just one of those guides that basically says "Use Action House" and that stuff, but it explains it a bit better than the others. Good luck! =)
